msgid "# Add-DnsServerRootHint"
msgstr "# Add-DnsServerRootHint"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Adds root hints on a DNS server."
msgstr "在DNS服务器上添加根提示（root hints）。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### InputObject (Default)"
msgstr "### InputObject（默认值）"

msgid "### Parameters"
msgstr "### 参数"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Add-DnsServerRootHint** cmdlet adds root hints on a Domain Name System (DNS) server.\n"
"You can add root hints by specifying the DNS name server and IP address, or you can use the *InputObject* parameter to specify a **DnsServerRootHint** object."
msgstr ""
"`Add-DnsServerRootHint` cmdlet 用于在域名系统（DNS）服务器上添加根提示信息。您可以通过指定 DNS 名称服务器和 IP"
" 地址来添加根提示信息，也可以使用 `InputObject` 参数来指定一个 `DnsServerRootHint` 对象。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Add a root hint to a DNS server by using IP address"
msgstr "### 示例 1：通过使用 IP 地址向 DNS 服务器添加根提示（root hint）"

msgid ""
"This command adds the IP address 172.23.90.128 for the name server "
"root.contoso.com to the list of root hints on the local DNS server."
msgstr ""
"该命令将 IP 地址 172.23.90.128 添加到本地 DNS 服务器上的根提示（root hints）列表中，用于名称服务器 "
"root.contoso.com。"

msgid ""
"### Example 2: Add a root hint to a DNS server by using an IPv6 address"
msgstr "### 示例 2：通过使用 IPv6 地址为 DNS 服务器添加根提示（root hint）"

msgid ""
"This command adds the IPv6 address 2001:4898:7020:f100:458f:e6a2:fcaf:698c "
"for the name server root.contoso.com to the list of root hints on the local "
"DNS server."
msgstr ""
"此命令将IPv6地址2001:4898:7020:f100:458f:e6a2:fCAF:698c添加到本地DNS服务器上的rootHints列表中，用于名称服务器root.contoso.com。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that"
" take a long time to complete."
msgstr "以后台作业的形式运行该cmdlet。使用此参数来执行那些需要较长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command prompt.\n"
"You can continue to work in the session while the job completes.\n"
"To manage the job, use the `*-Job` cmdlets.\n"
"To get the job results, use the [Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该cmdlet会立即返回一个表示该作业的对象，然后显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在当前会话中执行其他操作。要管理该作业，请使用`*-Job`系列的cmdlets；要获取作业的结果，请使用[Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about Windows PowerShell background jobs, see "
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 Windows PowerShell 后台作业的更多信息，请参阅 [关于作业（About "
"Jobs）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer.\n"
"Enter a computer name or a session object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967) or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet.\n"
"The default is the current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该cmdlet。请输入计算机名称或会话对象（例如，[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967) 或 [Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet "
"的输出结果）。默认值是本地计算机上的当前会话。"

msgid ""
"Specifies a remote DNS server.\n"
"You can specify an IP address or any value that resolves to an IP address, such as a fully qualified domain name (FQDN), host name, or NETBIOS name."
msgstr ""
"指定一个远程DNS服务器。您可以指定一个IP地址，或者任何能够解析为IP地址的值，例如完全限定域名（FQDN）、主机名或NETBIOS名称。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行cmdlet之前会提示您确认是否要执行该操作。"

msgid "Specifies an array of IPv4 or IPv6 addresses of DNS servers."
msgstr "指定一个包含DNS服务器IPv4或IPv6地址的数组。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the input to this cmdlet.\n"
"You can use this parameter, or you can pipe the input to this cmdlet."
msgstr "指定要传递给此 cmdlet 的输入数据。您可以使用该参数，也可以将输入数据通过管道（pipe）传递给该 cmdlet。"

msgid "Specifies the fully qualified domain name of the root name server."
msgstr "指定根名称服务器的完全限定域名（fully qualified domain name）。"

msgid ""
"Returns an object representing the item with which you are working.\n"
"By default, this cmdlet does not generate any output."
msgstr "返回一个对象，该对象表示您正在操作的项。默认情况下，此cmdlet不生成任何输出。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet.\n"
"If this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then Windows PowerShell® calculates an optimum throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the computer.\n"
"The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the computer."
msgstr ""
"指定可以同时运行的cmdlet的最大操作数量。如果省略此参数或输入`0`，则Windows PowerShell®会根据计算机上正在运行的CIM "
"cmdlet的数量来计算该cmdlet的最佳限制值。此限制仅适用于当前运行的cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行这个cmdlet。"

